          "date": "2022-06-14 04:08:14.000000000",
          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-15928 osd: pass keylen for dt index operations",
        "message": "LU-15928 osd: pass keylen for dt index operations\n\n*** WIP TODO ***\n- finish all function conversions\n- test random encrypted filenames to hit corner cases\n\nWith fscrypt passing binary names to the underlying ldiskfs storage,\nthe lookup API should be passing the length of the key through the\nDT index API instead of calling strlen() on the string, otherwise\nthis may incorrectly process keys with embedded NUL bytes.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: If62f30a202fad903d8b3b0de86cb252964ce7057\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
